==========================
Wipm
==========================

:Author:  Radomir Azizov

Purpose
-------
Wipm is a interactive graphical console for work with device that is running PyMite. 

License
-------
Wipm is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify
it under the terms of the GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 2.1.

Wipm is distributed in the hope that it will be useful,
but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of
MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.


Requirements
------------
Python 2.6.x
wxPython 2.9
Pyserial 2.6


-------------
Installation
-------------
You do not need to install Wipm.
You do need to have Python, Pyserial and wxPython installed.
(www.python.org, pyserial.sourceforge.net, www.wxpython.org).

Just run wipm.py

Tested On Windows7, Linux.


